title: Bobby Nervous About MRI Scan + Raymundo's 'Big Brother' Pitch + Country Music Press Conference
itunes:title: Bobby Nervous About MRI Scan + Raymundo's 'Big Brother' Pitch + Country Music Press Conference
description:
Bobby shares an update on his trip to the brain doctor, including being in the MRI machine for 30 minutes with crazy loud noises. Raymundo pitches himself to the casting director of 'Big Brother' hoping to realize a childhood dream. Plus, Bobby gives a press conference on the state of country music and what you can expect to happen with your favorite country artists in the coming months!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
